{"type":"decision-raised","node_id":"circuit-launch-sprint-2026-05-29","item_id":"cls-dec-email-account-constraint","text":"DECIDED 2026-05-29: Each email maps to ONE org + ONE user. C-47 implements as inline invite-UI warning � (a) \"this email already has an account\", (b) same-org vs different-org context with org name visible to inviter, (c) \"move account here\" affordance. No new screens.","actor":"gui","event_id":"01KSTVH3X85MH9PEYMVS1ET2DA","ts":"2026-05-29T21:51:30.216Z"}
