{"type":"action-added","node_id":"circuit-launch-sprint-2026-05-29","item_id":"cls-tier2-contact-delete","text":"Tier 2: Contact deletion/archive (verified gap � no DELETE handler at src/app/api/contacts/[id]/route.ts, bulk-action route supports only move_stage + send_message, no soft-delete fields, no UI delete button). Recommend soft-archive default. Owner-only with admin override per org policy. UI surfaces: contact detail (single), list (bulk), confirmation modal.","actor":"gui","event_id":"01KSTVH495J7980XVHXZ5Z3MNG","ts":"2026-05-29T21:51:30.597Z"}
{"type":"action-added","node_id":"circuit-launch-sprint-2026-05-29","item_id":"cls-s8-support-chatbot","text":"Tier 2: S8 � In-app support chatbot. Floating Help widget on every Circuit page. Phase 1 = Q&A over Support Pages MDX corpus. Phase 2 = tool-call extension (show-me-where-X-is, explain-this-error, summarize-org-state, whats-changed-recently). Uses Circuit LLM client. Per-user conversation history. Plugin interface for new tools. Was BLOCKED on S7 Phase 2 ? SHIPPED in PR #378 ? UNBLOCKED 2026-05-29.","actor":"gui","event_id":"01KSTVH4ED7H9N75MV8R7ACNZ2","ts":"2026-05-29T21:51:30.765Z"}
{"type":"decision-raised","node_id":"circuit-launch-sprint-2026-05-29","item_id":"cls-dec-contact-delete-shape","text":"DECIDED 2026-05-29: Contact deletion = soft-archive ONLY on contractor surface (archived_at, hidden from list/search, reversible by admin, audit trail preserved). Hard-delete reserved for verified CCPA requests via dedicated admin-only workflow (structured request log, 24-month retention, third-party vendor notification trigger). Hard-delete NOT exposed in regular contact UI.","actor":"gui","event_id":"01KSTW6AGYBRSPKF5F68BGD7BQ","ts":"2026-05-29T22:03:05.118Z"}
